{"tid":1860382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"武漢會展中心將改造成醫院，提供1000床位","createTime":"2020-02-03T15:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T19:10:22.000Z","uid":48040,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"587cebc9fa5502c59346d1accc5924707eae2b1b","tid":1860382,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"火神山、雷神山都唔夠啊，再整多個集中營。<br />\n<br />\n【殘體字預警】<br />\n<br />\n据悉，2月3日24时前，武汉国际会展中心将改造成为1000张床位的&ldquo;方舱医院&rdquo;。当天18时起，110名江汉区环卫工人进入武汉国际会展中心，清理所有杂物。随后，环卫工人把一楼、二楼进行清扫，洗扫车把地面全部清洗干净，垃圾全部清运。江汉区城管执法队派了60名队员，往会展中心内搬运病床。江汉城管还调了10台移动公厕到现场。硚口城管也派出队员，参与运输和搬运临时床具。截至21时45分，清扫、搬运工作仍在进行中。（湖北经视 (<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/1649173367/IsxAfxx8O?type=comment#_rnd1580743273137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2F1649173367%2FIsxAfxx8O%3Ftype%3Dcomment%23_rnd1580743273137&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=63e57ad3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/1649173367/IsxAfxx8O?type=comment#_rnd1580743273137</a>)）"},{"pid":"5d368c7f7d91a6fd4af6d6e49016e105c277defc","tid":1860382,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"遲啲改埋高鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457357af550b0fd376fe97aa90999147ad9d70c3","tid":1860382,"uid":48040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:28:57.000Z","msg":"一日冇足夠床位將全部疑似病人隔離，疫情都會不斷蔓延"},{"pid":"0d1b73c197d9c8c6dba2cc33c18ba06cb78dc26d","tid":1860382,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:30:45.000Z","msg":"唔係負壓病房有乜用?"},{"pid":"1316a7b29da7c44074f0be6aea05150e64c74f0f","tid":1860382,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:31:02.000Z","msg":"水神山 地神山 光神山  暗神山<br />\n<br />\n已經幫你改好名"},{"pid":"bd07dd611ffa51713032050bebf56aa03c67e517","tid":1860382,"uid":162535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTim